case_name: Three Affiliated Tribes of Fort Berthold Reservation v. Wold Engineering, P. C.
first_party: Three Affiliated Tribes of Fort Berthold Reservation
winning_party: Three Affiliated Tribes of Fort Berthold Reservation
advocate_description_2: for an Indian tribe such as petitioner to avail itself of the jurisdiction of North Dakota courts as a plaintiff, it must also accept the jurisdiction of those courts when it is properly named as a defendant in them
